{
  "texts": [
    "Admixture graph modeling and introgression analysisThe SNP dataset was filtered using '-mac 1 -max-alleles 2' in VCFtools [74] and '-indeppairwise 50 5 0.3' in plink [75], and the convert program from AdmixTools was used to produce eigenstrat format data files.",
    "In order to measure allele sharing of three or four sets of subpopulations and to report the |Z|-score between predicted and observed values, the f 3 and F ST statistics were computed using ADMIXTOOLS 2.0 (https:// uqrma ie1. github.",
    "io/ admix tools) [76].",
    "A heuristic algorithm to iteratively fit increasingly complex models, qpbrute (https:// github.",
    "com/ ekirv ing/ qpbru te) filtered 1,183 possible admixture graph models and recorded ten graphs that left no f 4 outliers (|Z| < 3) [77]."
  ]
}